Class ProxyOAuth20ServiceImpl

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.scribe.oauth.OAuth20ServiceImpl

  • All Implemented Interfaces:

    Direct Known Subclasses:
    FoursquareOAuth20ServiceImpl, PayPalOAuth20ServiceImpl, StateOAuth20ServiceImpl

    public class ProxyOAuth20ServiceImpl
extends org.scribe.oauth.OAuth20ServiceImpl
    This class represents a specific OAuth service with proxy capabilities for OAuth 2.0 protocol. It could be part of the Scribe library.
